provisions.content:
13. A person shall not, on the Campus-                                     vegetation,
      (a)   cut trees;                                                        etc.
      (b) take fruits from trees or plants;
      ( c) set fires or remove growing grass;
      (d) lay or put up any wire, cable, fence, pipeline, net or any
              other material;
      (e) dig, excavate, bore or lay any road, track or path, without
             being so authorized by the Committee.
